description: This 2-bed, 2.5-bath home is your oasis from the world with a private balcony and oversized window walls capturing tons of natural sunlight and breathtaking views of the harbor, skyline and downtown Seaport.  Residence 1108 includes a gourmet kitchen with custom white-gloss Italian cabinetry, quartz counters and Thermador appliances ensuring a space optimal for entertaining.  The den provides a work-from-home office or an added bedroom with the option to close off the space with opaque glass sliding doors.  The primary bedroom features a large en suite bathroom with marble floors and a custom walk-in closet while the second bedroom has an en suite bathroom.  Included extras are Lutron motorized window treatments, in-unit laundry, 40 sqft of private storage, and valet parking for 2.  Echelon residents enjoy a indoor basketball court, 3 pools, fitness center, golf simulator, yoga studio, spa, dog run, resident lounges, BBQ area, playroom, co-working space, and 24/7 5-star trained staff.
